Title: Hush WKWebView
Description: If you’re building an iOS app with webviews, you need to decide whether to use WKWebView or SFSafariViewController. On the other hand, the Safari version automatically gets some of the features of Safari like content blocking extensions, but customization options are pretty limited and it doesn’t support loading local HTML files.
